snippet.title: Call to Arms - Gates of Hell: Talvisota release teaser
snippet.description:
The acclaimed Gates of Hell RTS expands the realm of WWII realism with TALVISOTA, bringing the Finland nation, new revolutionary skirmish battles and countless maps and missions for multiplayer, singleplayer and dynamic campaign.

Real Time Strategy WWII DLC for Call to Arms - Gates of Hell: Ostfront, published june 2022
